		<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Philada</placeName> <date>July 22&#44; 1852</date>.</p>
		<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir&#58; Your favour of this morning<lb/> with Check for Eighty&#45;four Dollars enclosed&#44;<lb/> is received. Please receive our thanks for the<lb/> same. The statement of this account as ren&#45;<lb/>dered <date>April 1</date> left a balance at that date<lb/> of &#36;84.46 The account is now closed on our<lb/> books.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">The &#8220;Evidence&#8221; please find enclosed.</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Yours respectfully</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">for <persName role="author">C. Sherman</persName>&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">per <persName role="author">M. F. Benerman</persName></p>
          
        </body>
